summary: It's a Racemenu preset. Not much else to say.
descriptionHtml:
Just a couple presets with slight differences in body sizes for my own dark elf character.

Mods:
Racemenu by expired6978
Ethereal Elven Overhaul by nuska
CBBE by Caliente
CBBE SEAM FIX FOR Ethereal Elven Overhaul by Rayne72
SG Female Eyebrows by Hello Santa
KS Hairdos Renewal by Kalilies and Stealthic
(Eyebrow specularity fix by Sooner 266, !Might not be needed but I had to use it!)
Immersive Warpaints and Tattoos by Reptileye
KJ Tattoos and KJ Lore Tattoos (same download page) by Khajitas
The Coenaculi for CBBE/For Male (dunno if I used both by accident) by Desufire
The Eyes of Beauty by Gabriel Mailhot as LogRaam
(Lets hope I didn't miss one...)

Installation:
Just drop the files into your preset folder
file path:
Program Files (x86) > Steam > steamapps > common > Skyrim > Data > SKSE > Plugins > CharGen > Presets
